ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectJuan Pablo Rodriguez ** MP Travel **
PrecisOrder authorizing JUAN PABLO RODRIGUEZ, Member of Parliament for Honoré-Mercier, Quebec, to travel to Los Angeles, California, United States from September 7 to 10, 2017 for the purposes of informing ethnic communities about Canada’s asylum and immigration rules.
